histogram.summary:
Records various stages of the Autofill AI funnel. The same metric is logged for submitted and for abandoned forms, with an additional metric aggregating both. The metric is recorded once per form per submission/abandonment.
Note that the variant aggregated over all EntityTypes was emitted differently before M140 and then not emitted at all in M141, so data is most accurate starting from M142.
{FunnelStage}
{EntityGranularity}

Records various stages of the Autofill AI funnel. The same metric is logged
for submitted and for abandoned forms, with an additional metric aggregating
both. The metric is recorded once per form per submission/abandonment.

{FunnelStage}

